channel.title: The Forum Resistance [Canned/Spies Win]
channel.description:
**Welcome to the Dystopian world of Resistance. You along with your fellow resistance members are trying to take down the Imperials. However, someone, your fellow members are spies** (This is based on the game *The Resistance*. If anybody knows what that is, then you should know how to play.)
How it works. 1.There is a random leader and he chooses what people to go on the mission. (They can choose themselves) 2. After the leader has chosen the necessary amount of people, everybody, votes **PUBLICILY** on whether or not the mission should go. The option with the most amount of votes is what happens. 3. If the majority says yes. The mission happens... The Resistance members who are *not* spies must say it succeeds. **IF** there is a spy the can choose for it to fail. **One fail card can fail the mission** If it succeeds the resistance gets a point. If it fails the spies get a point. The first to thee points to win. IF the majority says no. The leader ships passes down. 5 rejected missions in a row and the spies automatically win.
Every phase takes 24 hours. **PLAYERS** 1. @finnhorizon 2. @Moleland 3. @Simon 4. @Insanity 5. @Sketch 6. @Hippolytus 7. @Rogue 8. @PokemonKidRyan 9. @Icibalus 10. ~~@JammySplodge~~(MODKILLED. [color=steblue] Resistance Member [/color]) 11. Wolfy 12. Unknown **BACK-UPS** Eevee
To join say **/join** Or something along those lines. Also, A Co-host would be nice if anybody would volunteer for that. **Credits** The awesome people who made the Table top game first. Any and all people who try this out. This *might* fall flat on it's face
